dcterms:description: The LPBA40 dataset is composed of a series of maps from the regions of the brain, containing 40 T1-weighted 3D brain images from healthy volunteers, with manual segmentation to identify 56 structures.
dcterms:title: LONI Probabilistic Brain Atlas (LPBA40)

dcterms:description: The MindBoggle101 dataset consists of a collection of 101 T1-weighted 3D brain MRIs from healthy subjects, with manual segmentation masks for 50 anatomical labels.
dcterms:title: MindBoggle101
